snippet.title: Converting Fractions to Decimals [fbt]
snippet.description:
This video by Fort Bend Tutoring shows the process of converting fractions into decimals. Eight (8) examples are shown in this FBT math tutorial. This video is instructed by Larry "Mr. Whitt" Whittington. Intro/Outro by Chuck Knipp's Shirley Q. Liquor.
